  "title": "Green Axolotl X Axolotl Buckets",
  "description": "Adds a new green axolotl variant that can spawn naturally in Minecraft and supports axolotl bucket variants via the Axolotl Buckets mod.",
  "body": "<p align=\"center\">Adds the long-awaited green axolotl to Minecraft, a variant shown in official clips but never added to the game.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a76a8133887bffb2b495004872512939354f0e6b.png\" alt=\"Green Axolotl Title\" width=\"900\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\">Axolotl bucket variants match the axolotl you pick up.</p>\n<hr>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/369121c09b2bf51e6bffc9d060af47d32f2bc779.png\" alt=\"Sample\" width=\"200\"></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a537c7bd782868705556321fbb64b55e3c9002ce.png\" alt=\"Axolotl Buckets\" width=\"500\"></a></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/0d1068c67cd2beaafe71a71252b5f271f535de89.png\" alt=\"Green Axolotl\" width=\"300\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/green-axolotll\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/9d3cd7c29b765ea051a12413a8580e6b002c04ff.png\" alt=\"Modrinth Download Button\" width=\"300\"></a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/patrickool/projects\"><img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/425e2c3a8f7ca6ba05b2d4ea767640abc7b5ae71.png\" alt=\"CurseForge Download Button\" width=\"300\"></a></p>",
